# Full-Stack Workflow

1. Read nna.config.yaml before any feature work
2. For new features, act as Integration Orchestrator (see docs/agents/integration-orchestrator.md)
3. Order: shared types → backend module → security review → frontend → security review → doctor
4. **Ask user** when frontend route, admin vs public, or API-only scope is unclear
5. Update nna.config.yaml features registry after completing a feature
6. Run pnpm doctor and pnpm test before finishing

No CLI generate commands — write code directly following docs/patterns/
